Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:30.18,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(200,0)}Vermelha 12年前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko總是陪在你身邊 沒有也無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}下面節目是最新消息「News Room」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}現在Vermelha市內Monstro Preto的存在非常醒目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}之前失蹤的主要成員的尸體被不斷發現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}與其敵對勢力Fantasma之間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}發生大規模沖突的可能性非常高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起拍照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 還是不要喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經干掉10瓶了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 放我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！ 放我下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要退出Monstro
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我去見Satoshi君了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃也沒有用 我一定會去追你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是屬于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}104號巴士前往Sao Marcelo的乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}現在開始檢票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬣狗們的嘉年華會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Terra 四月13日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我好找啊 Manabe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么呀 難道不記得我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說點什么呀 你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開車
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話就在這里談
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓老子不爽啊 你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直沒睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開車
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼去哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.86,0:06:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面玩 還沒回家...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 你那邊怎么樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么把Michiko送上列車
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這邊做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去收保護費
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 那種無聊的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shinsuke 你丫說什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是老大？ 啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.07,0:06:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會歧視別人 也不會對某些人特別照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大只要一個就夠了 我最強
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是個馬仔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我不是Monstro的總統
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被你弄哭的光腳丫的Satoshi Batista
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chazz 把這個藏到Michi的衣服里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“誰是真正的強者”游戲開幕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我賭她了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣好的話 Satoshi君就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上會到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko會在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該在來這里的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是由Shinsuke負責的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 她沒死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ricardo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃變更 去Terra
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.25,0:08:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當年的我 有點不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會說 讓你放過我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的老婆和兒子無論如何請...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫真的能死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 開什么玩笑 Manabe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.91,0:09:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當年你不是兢兢業業的在履行老大的職責嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人、斗毆、買藥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說不是很平常嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想重要的親人死掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Manaba 現在就按我說的話去做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個小時之內會有列車過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車里會有個慘兮兮的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.39,0:09:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼的未來就在你的手上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這個孩子沒有關系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要人質 就我一個人好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了算的是本大爺 不要對老子發號施令！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 你丫幾歲了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10歲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經長毛了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fad(50,200)}Diarreia 25年前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！ 等等！ 臭小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi Morenos
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.33,0:11:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Satoshi Batista
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 長毛了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點點...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經長的很茂密了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經是成年人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi 我會成為老大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搶Manabe的組織 占領他的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時你能幫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是總統
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是總統助理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shinsuke 干過頭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們 在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個去哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.82,0:12:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在煙抽完之前 逗我笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣也許我不會要你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以前你對我做過的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什么 一點意思都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困 Manabe那時你也睡不著覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做老大的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這表情不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加把勁 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四周都是敵人 沒有人可以信任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想殺Manabe的Satoshi被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們情況不妙 被抓住的話會被一起殺掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 有誰帶煙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我抽完這根之前 逗我笑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 我就不要你的命了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要兩條腿 就饒了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里不是廁所 臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我剛才笑了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 拿刀來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰去拿把刀 鋒利的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 找我有什么事情 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道Hiroshi的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有找你了 可以打聽的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他坐的巴士爆炸了的事情 你也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒焦的尸體我可是親眼看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:15:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了 他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你從他那里聽到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Monstro的首腦們全部被我收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后嫁禍給Fantasma 把Fantasma搞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.59,0:15:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有地盤就都是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命名為“電擊百慕大三角作戰”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我頭腦真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我想出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好土
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你在Fantasma的地盤四處搗亂 Kiril說想見我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么和解協定的 管我屁事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.79,0:15:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一刀捅下去時 立刻見上帝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面正是要大顯身手的時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi那個家伙居然說不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是要和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我造出Kiril失蹤的假象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為退出的條件 讓他去找出Kiril
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下只要把礙事的你收拾掉就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不在的話 就不會變成這樣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.86,0:16:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shinsuke 你丫干的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 不要射偏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里 或者是這里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了早晨 你也就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你賣給Atsuko了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi還活著 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 他在哪里我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\fad(50,50)}四月14日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個old school風格的禿頭是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的可愛部下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他一個吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃色太陽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.39,0:17:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動！ Satoshi Batista！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四周已經被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Atsuko 你丫！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向當地警署請求了支援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在問你怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不要動 這是我的案子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次如果讓Michiko Malandro跑掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會受到降職處分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心 Michiko我會抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部 我是在說我不想再給你擦屁股了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪著比自己年輕的女警部亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心情你能理解嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有家庭 剛蓋的房子還有貸款要還
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪你殉葬的想法 可是連這么一點點也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.11,0:18:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降職 抱歉我想都沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我負責指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是Michiko Malandro和Satoshi Batista兩名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:19:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格均很兇殘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有需要的話 可以射殺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行動要冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ricardo！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可以和你拜拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家就安穩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩名犯人逃跑中 立即追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 我去支援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是目標 是田鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重復一遍 不是目標 是田鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慘的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算向我開槍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我走吧 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 事關我的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是朋友吧 Atsuko
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧 這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用沒有子彈的槍指著我有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko Malandro是這樣的女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了激怒對方 說點Jumbo什么的廢話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后揍倒我 逃跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會射擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.19,0:21:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警部
